# Expertise knowledge base — DI-COMMIT (markdown summary, bukan PDF mentah)
!data/expertise/
data/expertise/_raw_*.txt

# Brand configs — fotofusi demo committed, brand lain tidak
config/brands/*.config.json
!config/brands/fotofusi.config.json
!config/brands/_schema.md

